What secrets?

587
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:18,100
What secrets do you have?

588
00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:19,380
Don't be annoying.

589
00:25:20,180 --> 00:25:22,140
First, at Old Lady's birthday party...

590
00:25:22,260 --> 00:25:23,820
Oh no. Shut up.

591
00:25:24,380 --> 00:25:26,140
Other maids will stop

592
