593
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:29,620
But you slip out everything.

594
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,460
Don't be Mingxia.

595
00:25:30,460 --> 00:25:31,580
Be Ms. Loose-lipped.

596
00:25:31,940 --> 00:25:33,900
I'm not loose-lipped.

597
00:25:35,380 --> 00:25:36,900
Get out of here.

598
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,060
She's just ignorant.

599
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,060
Don't be angry with her.

600
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:40,460
Or it may drive you mad.

601
00:25:41,780 --> 00:25:43,660
Mother, if you ask me,

602
