791
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,340
Sorry, I have the wrong person.

792
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:47,940
It's alright. I'm honored.

793
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:49,260
I really am.

794
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,220
Stand there.

795
00:32:50,540 --> 00:32:51,380
Who are they?

796
00:32:51,380 --> 00:32:52,500
- Why here?
- Letter.

797
00:32:52,500 --> 00:32:54,100
Get out of here.

798
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:55,620
- I'll explain to you.
- Get out.

799
00:32:55,620 --> 00:32:56,620
Let me explain!

800
00:32:58,420 --> 00:32:59,820
I'll explain to you.

801
00:33:12,540 --> 00:33:14,140
Fine. You get some rest.

802
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,180
She's coming out.

803
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:19,660
Wanqing, how was it going?

804
00:33:19,860 --> 00:33:21,500
Don't worry. He'll teach you.

805
00:33:21,780 --> 00:33:22,700
Brilliant.

806
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:24,300
Thank you, Wanqing.

807
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:25,980
Without you, our trip would be in vain.

808
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:27,220
Thank you.

809
00:33:31,420 --> 00:33:32,460
I nearly slapped him.

810
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:33,500
Yeah. Look.

811
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,020
- What's wrong?
- High five.

812
00:33:35,460 --> 00:33:36,420
What high five?

813
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,700
Nothing.

814
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:42,860
Luo Zhusi.

815
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,140
Xue Muyun.

816
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:45,700
Old Lady.

817
00:33:47,420 --> 00:33:48,580
They're in this position.

818
00:33:49,420 --> 00:33:50,460
And I...

819
00:33:55,940 --> 00:33:57,140
This is me.

820
00:33:57,980 --> 00:33:59,380
Yes. This is my position.

821
00:34:01,080 --> 00:34:01,940
Do you know

822
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:03,340
