830
00:34:17,860 --> 00:34:18,940
That night,

831
00:34:19,060 --> 00:34:21,060
I saw him come back really late.

832
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:22,300
And he burned something.

833
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:24,420
Do you think he's...?

834
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:26,540
Walls have ears.

835
00:34:26,740 --> 00:34:27,660
Let's talk over there.

836
00:34:36,740 --> 00:34:37,660
Luo Aji?

837
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:46,140
(Fu's Restaurant)

838
00:34:46,140 --> 00:34:47,940
Waiter, the bill, please.

839
00:34:50,460 --> 00:34:51,780
Down there.

840
00:35:05,860 --> 00:35:06,820
Do you know what I did

841
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:07,780
last night?

842
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:09,900
You know what?

843
00:35:10,180 --> 00:35:11,100
I can't

844
00:35:11,420 --> 00:35:13,420
be very nice to her.

845
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:14,980
She offended me.

846
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:16,940
What should we men be like?

847
00:35:17,140 --> 00:35:18,180
- What?
- What?

848
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:20,100
Sugarcane.

849
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,620
Sugarcane?

850
00:35:21,940 --> 00:35:23,100
First sweet,

851
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,900
and then unfaithful.

852
00:35:29,060 --> 00:35:30,500
Sweet and then unfaithful.

853
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:31,460
Indeed.

854
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:33,100
- Very wise.
- Sweet and unfaithful.

855
00:35:33,100 --> 00:35:34,100
Luo Aji.

856
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:37,420
Why are you here?

857
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:39,020
You said you had something to do.

858
00:35:39,020 --> 00:35:40,100
So, it's drinking with them?

859
00:35:41,020 --> 00:35:41,980
Yes.

860
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:43,300
Isn't it important?

861
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:45,180
Do you know when you're here,

862
00:35:45,180 --> 00:35:46,580
